This paper discusses the use of XML data warehousing and OLAP analyses on XML data cubes, which are topics related to databases (cs.DB) and information retrieval (cs.IR). The paper also proposes a rollup operator based on a pattern tree, which involves algorithms and data structures that are relevant to deep learning (cs.DL), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), and machine learning (cs.LG).
